3.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T13:18:36.000Z","msg":"好撚好食 想食翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T13:58:45.000Z","msg":"係好L好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99a68166561c5707abc7e8d0deb6aa25ffd56211","tid":891790,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27174d144b579af9874da6401917eaf4cae5a9eb","tid":891790,"uid":1762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e92c0844c7c3747cc842378f059b0899dacecaa1","tid":891790,"uid":149793,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T11:39:25.000Z","msg":"以前2月去過，兩件羽絨走唔甩，夜晚隨時零下二十幾三十度。要買定對雪靴，普通鞋會凍到腳趾痛。"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T11:40:58.000Z","msg":"雪靴有無推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗住買timberland <br />\n但係太貴"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T14:18:16.000Z","msg":"鞋淘寶貨二百左右夠做"},{"pid":"3468a2b68b52e050cdcdaf5d6296f4b548d4b19d","tid":891790,"uid":123631,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T14:21:29.000Z","msg":"試過喺當地發燒，夜晚去完冰雪大世界返嚟凍到退咗燒"},{"pid":"4cacd82e84154e281a9ba1913c44b6cb53806996","tid":891790,"uid":56807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T15:07:47.000Z","msg":"想平又有得睇去迪卡龍買，不過之前未在香港開舖上大陸官網買比現價重平，不過你會發現成日同人撞衫。"},{"pid":"0dea4fdebaf01e5a164f53760ecb1e6529eebbcc","tid":891790,"uid":136086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T15:26:53.000Z","msg":"值唔值得去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"302a1204cab4f1c37ce9a126144906b45d1aa8d0","tid":891790,"uid":1762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T11:28:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d62690f222946dd695bc9d0e330c7f2f152623bb","tid":891790,"uid":87209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"302a1204cab4f1c37ce9a126144906b45d1aa8d0